Insider Activity


Individual




Hubert de Pesquidoux



Mr. Hubert de Pesquidoux is Independent Director at Criteo SA, Independent Director at RadiSys Corp., Independent Director at Mavenir Systems, Inc., and Independent Director at Sequans Communications SA. He is on the Board of Directors at Criteo SA, RadiSys Corp., Mavenir Systems, Inc., Sequans Communications SA, Criteo Corp., and Transaction Network Services, Inc.
Mr. de Pesquidoux was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer by HDP Consulting LLC, Chairman by Tekelec Global, Inc., CFO & President-Enterprise Business Group by Alcatel-Lucent SA, Chief Executive Officer by Alcatel Canada, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Alcatel-Lucent Holdings, Inc., a Director & Executive Vice President by Alcatel, Inc., Executive Partner by SIRIS Capital Group LLC, President & Chief Operating Officer by Alcatel-Lucent USA, Inc., and Treasurer by Alcatel Alsthom, Inc. He also served on the board at AlbaixEnergies, Inc. and Tactical Network Solutions LLC.
He received his graduate degree from Sciences Po, a graduate degree from Université Paris Dauphine, and a graduate degree from Université Nancy 2.



